<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About IAAI - International Aesthetic Academic Institution</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Breadcrumb */
        .breadcrumb {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .breadcrumb-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #002147;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        .breadcrumb span {
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #002147 0%, #003366 100%);
            padding: 120px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Ccircle cx='30' cy='30' r='2'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-weight: 400;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Statistics Section */
        .stats-section {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 80px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .stats-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .content-section {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b, #002147);
        }

        .section-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .section-content {
            padding: 60px;
        }

        .section-content h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-content h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
        }

        .section-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-content ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .section-content li {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-content li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #ffcc00;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .section-image {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 400px;
        }

        .section-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .section-image:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Services Grid */
        .services-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .services-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-title p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .service-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
        }

        .service-header {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-features {
            padding: 0 30px 30px;
        }

        .service-features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .service-features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .service-features li::before {
            content: '•';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #ffcc00;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .service-cta {
            padding: 0 30px 30px;
        }

        .service-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
            color: #002147;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .service-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.4);
        }

        /* Technology Section */
        .technology-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #002147, #003366);
            padding: 80px 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .technology-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .tech-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .tech-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tech-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .tech-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .tech-card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .tech-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        /* Instructors Preview */
        .instructors-section {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .instructors-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .instructors-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .instructor-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .instructor-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .instructor-avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .instructor-card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .instructor-card h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .instructor-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Learning Paths Section */
        .learning-paths-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .paths-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .path-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 5px solid #ffcc00;
        }

        .path-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .path-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
            color: #002147;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .path-card h4 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .path-steps {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .path-steps li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .path-steps li::before {
            content: '→';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #ffcc00;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcc00, #b8860b);
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #002147;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background: #002147;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 33, 71, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 33, 71, 0.5);
            background: #001a3a;
        }

        .cta-btn.secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #002147;
            color: #002147;
        }

        .cta-btn.secondary:hover {
            background: #002147;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Values Section */
        .values-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #002147, #003366);
            padding: 80px 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .values-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .values-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .value-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .value-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ffcc00;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .value-card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .value-card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .section-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .section-content {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            .section-content h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .stats-container {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .services-grid,
            .instructors-grid,
            .values-grid,
            .tech-grid,
            .paths-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }

        /* Animation */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <div class="breadcrumb-container">
            <a href="/">Home</a> > <span>About Us</span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Leading the Future of Aesthetic Medicine Education</h1>
            <p>International Aesthetic Academic Institution (IAAI) is the world's premier destination for comprehensive aesthetic medicine training, certification, and professional development across multiple modalities and global locations.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Statistics Section -->
    <section class="stats-section">
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">5,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Trained Professionals</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-award"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Training Programs</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">75+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Countries Served</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">4.9/5</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Average Rating</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Expert Instructors</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                <div class="stat-icon"><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i></div>
                <div class="stat-number">15,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Certificates Issued</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <!-- Mission Section -->
        <div class="content-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-grid">
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p><strong>Empowering Aesthetic Excellence Worldwide.</strong> We are dedicated to advancing the field of aesthetic medicine through comprehensive education, innovative training methodologies, and internationally recognized certification programs.</p>
                    <p>Our mission is to equip healthcare professionals with the knowledge, skills, and confidence needed to deliver exceptional patient care while driving innovation in aesthetic medicine across the globe.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="section-image">
                    <img src="/images/mission.jpg" alt="Our Mission">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision Section -->
        <div class="content-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-grid">
                <div class="section-image">
                    <img src="/images/vision.jpg" alt="Our Vision">
                </div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                    <p><strong>Shaping the Global Standard for Aesthetic Education.</strong> To be the world's leading authority in aesthetic medicine education, recognized for excellence, innovation, and transformative impact on the industry.</p>
                    <p>We envision a future where every aesthetic professional has access to world-class training, enabling them to achieve exceptional results while advancing evidence-based practices globally.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
        <div class="content-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-grid">
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Why Choose IAAI?</h2>
                    <p>Our commitment to excellence and comprehensive approach sets us apart in aesthetic medicine education:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Internationally recognized expert instructors with decades of experience</li>
                        <li>Multiple training modalities: In-person, Live Online, and Self-paced learning</li>
                        <li>Premium global locations: Istanbul, Dubai, and Verona, Italy</li>
                        <li>Comprehensive certification programs with international accreditation</li>
                        <li>State-of-the-art facilities and latest medical technologies</li>
                        <li>Small class sizes ensuring personalized attention and mentorship</li>
                        <li>Ongoing support through our digital learning platform</li>
                        <li>Global professional network and career advancement opportunities</li>
                        <li>Comprehensive assessment and quality assurance systems</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="section-image">
                    <img src="/images/choose-us.jpg" alt="Why Choose IAAI">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Comprehensive Services Section -->
    <section class="services-section">
        <div class="services-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Comprehensive Training Solutions</h2>
                <p>From foundational courses to advanced specializations, we offer complete educational pathways for aesthetic medicine professionals at every career stage.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="services-grid">
                <!-- In-Person Training -->
                <div class="service-card fade-in">
                    <div class="service-header">
                        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
                        <h3>In-Person Aesthetic Training</h3>
                        <p>Immersive hands-on training with direct patient interaction and expert supervision in premium medical facilities.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-features">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Live patient treatments under expert guidance</li>
                            <li>Advanced injection techniques and safety protocols</li>
                            <li>Facial anatomy and aesthetic assessment</li>
                            <li>PRP therapy and regenerative treatments</li>
                            <li>Chemical peels and skin rejuvenation</li>
                            <li>Laser treatments and energy-based devices</li>
                            <li>Complication management and emergency protocols</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-cta">
                        <a href="/in-person-aesthetic-training" class="service-btn">
                            Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Online Live Training -->
                <div class="service-card fade-in">
                    <div class="service-header">
                        <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-video"></i></div>
                        <h3>Live Online Training</h3>
                        <p>Interactive real-time training sessions with world-class instructors, featuring live demonstrations and Q&A.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-features">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Real-time interaction with expert instructors</li>
                            <li>HD video demonstrations and case studies</li>
                            <li>Live Q&A and personalized feedback</li>
                            <li>Interactive assessments and evaluations</li>
                            <li>Digital resource libraries and materials</li>
                            <li>Flexible scheduling across time zones</li>
                            <li>Recording access for review and reference</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
